 <text>
  <front>
   <head>An ODE To SLEEP</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">COME, gentle God of soft Repose,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And charm my Soul to Rest;</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">In thy Embraces let me lose</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">The Cares that rack my Breast.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Arise, ye dear Deceits, arise,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And drest in  Form,</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">My long-expecting, wishing Eyes</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">With his Resemblance charm.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Those melting Sounds still let me hear,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Which did his Flame impart;</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Which blest with Love my list'ning Ear,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And pierc'd my yielding Heart.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Why rove my Thoughts on fancied Bliss</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Which only Dreams bestow;</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">For oh whene'er the Morn appears,</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">I wake to real Woe.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="5" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The envious Light from my sad Eyes,</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Drives all my Bliss away;</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">With Night the lovely Phantom flies,</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And leaves me lost in Day.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="6" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="21" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Since waking then I am distrest,</l>
     <l n="22" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And Pleasure's fled with him;</l>
     <l n="23" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">If sleeping I can still be blest,</l>
     <l n="24" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Let Life be all a Dream.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
